Make sure to go on each coin's chart, select optimal bar size and then create these alerts for it. Pause each alert as you create them and unpause all at once in the end.


ETH

Cover Short and Fresh Long

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
a=* b=short c=position q=100% e=binancefutures s=ethusdt t=market
delay=1
a=* b=buy e=binancefutures l=1 q=10% y=equity s=ethusdt t=market
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Cover Long and Fresh Short

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
a=* b=long c=position q=100% e=binancefutures s=ethusdt t=market
delay=1
a=* b=sell e=binancefutures l=1 q=10% y=equity s=ethusdt t=market
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////



